nodes.text: The High Republic 9 is the forthcoming ninth issue of the comic book series Star Wars: The High Republic. The issue will be written by Cavan Scott, illustrated by Ario Anindito, and published by Marvel Comics on September 1, 2021.
A NEW STORY BEGINS THIS ISSUE – THE SHADOW OF THE NIHIL!
